    "The LLM serves as the teacher model with frozen parameters and the prediction model temp is the student model with parameters θ.",
    "The zi, hi are structured EHR and clinical text embedding generated by LLM and temp respectively.",
    "As each patient has structured EHR and clinical text, the zi, hi from the same patient Pi are highly related.",
    "On the other hand, the EHR and clinical text from different patients shares little common information for which the embeddings should have larger distance.",
